snippet.title: Wildkeepers Rising - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Wildkeepers Rising is an ✨innovative✨ bullet heaven:
🐉Collect and fight with a team of monsters
🕹️Directly control their special abilities
🗺️ Complex maps, not flat planes
🗡RPG campaign
👹Still defeat hordes of enemies!

Wishlist it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2995560/Wildkeepers_Rising/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=rda
